*JOU NIELSEN*
Jou Nielsen is an artist on a mission to share his passion for deep melodic and emotional music to the world.

With over a decade of experience in the underground music scene, Jou has honed his skills as Music Producer developing a reputation as a DJ in the industry. His dedication to his craft and love for music have earned him the opportunity to play at some renowned international venues including:

Pacha Barcelona, Nikki Beach Koh Samui, Hollystone, Mayan Beach Club, Salud Goa, Escobar Festival, Leo Beach Music Festival, Elrow, Bailamos Pune, The Bongo Club, Macarena Club, Jacqueline, Upload, 303 Audiophile and the iconic Full Moon Party at Moonrise Koh Phangan amongst others.

Jou achieved several Beatport Top 10 entries, including Mentalism EP, which held the #1 spot in Progressive House releases for over a week.artists from all over the globe.
